title.label: Edit: iPadOS not safe.. Fantastic Game Finally on Mobile!

content.label:
Edit: The iPadOS version of this app is currently broken in a scary way. I have two accounts I play on, no matter which one I log into, I get logged into only one of my characters. I haven’t tried with a friend, but i believe if someone else logged into their account on my iPad, they would be signed into my character! I believe if I let someone use my iPad my account would be at risk.. I’ve uninstalled and re-downloaded the app and the problem continues. I left an in-game bug report with no reply thus far. If this gets fixed I’ll update my review. 

If you’ve played RuneScape before, and you know what to expect! Runs great on the iPhone/iPad so far, and they will only improve it. 

If you’ve never played, you’re in for quite the ride... The osrs wiki will be your friend! Watch some YouTube videos and read some guides online to help with any quests or training skills! There are a lot of tricksters who play this game, so try not to get scammed! If you see “doubling money”, RUN! 

Jagex has a long history of regular updates and I think adding the game to mobile will prove to be a great and worthwhile addition.
